## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="a160e-103">Объект `SpeechHypothesized` событие <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer> и <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine> классы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a160e-103">A `SpeechHypothesized` event is raised by the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer> and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine> classes.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="a160e-104">Подробные сведения о предварительно распознанной фразы можно получить с помощью <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognitionEventArgs.Result%2A> свойство.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a160e-104">You can obtain detailed information about a tentatively recognized phrase by using the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognitionEventArgs.Result%2A> property.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="a160e-105">Многочисленные `SpeechHypothesized` события создаются как распознавание модуль пытается определить входной фразы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a160e-105">Numerous `SpeechHypothesized` events are generated as a recognition engine attempts to identify an input phrase.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a160e-106">Как правило обработка этих событий полезно только для отладки.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a160e-106">Typically, handling these events is useful only for debugging.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="a160e-107">Интерфейс `SpeechHypothesizedEventArgs` является производным от интерфейса <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognitionEventArgs>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a160e-107">`SpeechHypothesizedEventArgs` derives from <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognitionEventArgs>.</span></span>  



## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="a160e-108">В приведенном ниже примере создается обработчик <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.SpeechHypothesized?displayProperty=nameWithType> или <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.SpeechHypothesized?displayProperty=nameWithType> события.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a160e-108">The example below creates a handler for <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.SpeechHypothesized?displayProperty=nameWithType> or <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.SpeechHypothesized?displayProperty=nameWithType> events.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a160e-109">Экземпляр использует обработчик `SpeechHypothesizedEventArgs` для возврата и отображения сведений о условно распознанной фразы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a160e-109">The handler uses an instance of `SpeechHypothesizedEventArgs` to return and display information about a tentatively recognized phrase.</span></span>  

```  
// Create a handler for the SpeechHypothesized event.  
recognizer.SpeechHypothesized += new EventHandler<SpeechHypothesizedEventArgs>(recognizer_SpeechHypothesized);  

// Handle the event and display the hypothesized result.  
void recognizer_SpeechHypothesized (object sender, SpeechHypothesizedEventArgs e)  
  {  
    Console.WriteLine("Hypothesized text: " + e.Result.Text);  
  }  

```
